Key to species of 
<taxonomicName box="[366,509,762,789]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Plesiochara" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="517" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
